\section{General Information}
\begin{itemize}
\item Test run on a MacBook Pro, 2,4 GHz Intel Core i7, 8GB RAM. 
\item Maude version: 2.7.1 built: Oct  2 2017.
\item The search procedure considers proofs using up to 4 times the copy rule (focusing on one of the formulas of the classical context). Benchmarks 23 and 25 required the limit to be 5. 
\end{itemize}
